Collection
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Akimov, Alexandr
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The Discussion Paper Series in Accounting and Business Law represents work in progress on a range of accounting and business law-related issues. The papers are also published to the Research Papers in Economics (RePEc) web database of working papers, journals articles and software components.
